==Entrances==
* In [[Level 94]] you can enter by walking through a derelict shopping outlet that still plays soft mall music.
* In [[Level 186]] you can enter by stepping into a large mirrored department store that leads nowhere.
* In [[Level 200]] you can enter by following signs marked “PROMOTII” until they no longer update.
* Having a karma rating of -41 to -60 in [[Level 995]] will possibly lead you here.

==Exits==
* There's a slight chance that a shutter with a white glow may be open. If you enter that shutter, you'll end up in [[The Delta Mall]]
* Climbing a vent has a chance to lead you to [[Level 33]] or [[Level 22]]
